This plugin will automatically insert your ad code into the page content with random position between the existing paragraphs.

### Usage

Open `lot\worker\content.php` then put your AD code there.

To disable the automatic AD placement on certain page, add a `rapic` property with a value that can be evaluated to `false`:

~~~ .yaml
---
title: Page Title
description: Page description.
author: Taufik Nurrohman
type: HTML
rapic: false
...
~~~

